{"tid":2353293,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] 登記Apple ID時入錯email","createTime":"2021-01-04T15:20:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T15:45:14.000Z","uid":128514,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"641e28c73a24e0361b76c0a51e9b60b257edc48f","tid":2353293,"uid":128514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:20:52.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n剛才幫老爸登記Apple account 喺apple ID一欄入錯左email<br />\n本來應該係XXXX@yahoo.com.hk 但我入左XXXX@yahoo.com, <a href=\"http://即係冇左.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%8D%B3%E4%BF%82%E5%86%87%E5%B7%A6.hk&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=18c765b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">即係冇左.hk</a><br />\n之後我再重新用返正確既email再登記多一次, 但個系統似乎已經認到係同一個email, 無法使用<br />\n而家卡咗喺驗證嗰關, 但驗證碼只會send去我輸入apple ID個email到<br />\n未驗證之前想登入改返個email 但又徒勞無功, 佢話搵唔到呢個apple ID<br />\n<br />\n已經Google 搵過類似嘅個案, 都係教返我登入apple ID再修改email address, 但而家連驗證都驗證唔到仲點改?<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲打有冇試過出過類似問題, 最後又係點搞?"},{"pid":"47a9e5d274cb784b24867b2d5a26d9d6feaa7b80","tid":2353293,"uid":12908,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:23:35.000Z","msg":"開個無hk尾嘅yahoo email 得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f6b40bc8675133dcd98e87d3bf1258269692f1","tid":2353293,"uid":50123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:24:31.000Z","msg":"點解唔問直接apple..."},{"pid":"556dfb4384f30f7e213a3116f8bc6533167e0dc9","tid":2353293,"uid":128514,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73f6b40bc8675133dcd98e87d3bf1258269692f1","tid":2353293,"uid":50123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:24:31.000Z","msg":"點解唔問直接apple..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:27:08.000Z","msg":"本來想打電話問客服, 但而家收左工"},{"pid":"e26aa9da9a90931c51d67cdaa08558e474ce3823","tid":2353293,"uid":73179,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:28:36.000Z","msg":"俾返個Apple ID人啦"},{"pid":"59ef4bc7e382